analysis_result.summary: The document consists of four rental agreements for properties in different locations. The first property is in Villa No. 12, Lakeview Enclave, Whitefield, Bengaluru, owned by Mrs. Kavita Rao. The tenant, Mr. Arvind Menon, pays a monthly rent of INR 45,000 and a maintenance charge of INR 3,500. The security deposit is INR 1,50,000. The second property is in Villa No. 45, Green Valley Residency, Gachibowli, Hyderabad, but the agreement details are not provided. The third property is in Flat No. 502, Ocean Heights, Andheri West, Mumbai, owned by Mr. Ashok Gupta. The tenant, Mr. Rahul Desai, pays INR 60,000 as monthly rent and INR 5,000 as maintenance charge. The security deposit is INR 2,00,000. The fourth property is in Flat No. 302, Rose Residency, Baner, Pune, owned by Mr. Rajesh Sharma. The tenant, Ms. Priya Nair, pays INR 25,000 as monthly rent and INR 2,000 as maintenance charge. The security deposit is INR 75,000. All agreements are subject to specific durations and witnessed by designated individuals.
